reviews.review_text: Goin' to Kansas City This show flat-out rocks, with great sound quality (thanks Charlie Miller, etal). Excellent Scarlet>Fire and Estimated>Eyes, so don't miss this one!
This show is excellent Worth a listen
Thanks again, Charlie! Another great Dead experience!  When will we be seeing the "Charlie's Picks" series?

Bread crumb trail two years into a quest to listen to every recorded moment of live dead, it occured to me to leave a trail behind.

Nice show, the bitter end of Keith & Donna.  By this point in time, a good audience recording is every bit as satisfying as a SBD.  Very nice Scarlet > Fire
